Cinelerra-CV is the community version of the non-linear video editor Cinelerra, which was 
originally written by Heroine Virtual Ltd.

Cinelerra-CV is maintained through a community effort: http://cinelerra-cv.org.

This package was put together using sources obtained from:
git://git.cinelerra-cv.org/CinelerraCV.git

